Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:33.60,Dialogue,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, čuo sam glasine na putu od Lubinhajgena.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:35.65,Dialogue,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, da, strašno je.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.65,0:00:38.94,Dialogue,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li to pričate o čarobnjaku koji se pojavio na novom putu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:41.30,Dialogue,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čuo sam tu priču.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:45.10,Dialogue,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažu da može da prizove vukove i manipuliše njima po svojoj volji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:48.51,Dialogue,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oni napadaju putnike kako bi pili njihovu krv.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:49.73,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije valjda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.59,0:00:54.58,Dialogue,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Istina je. Bolje je da budete oprezni.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.58,0:00:58.41,Dialogue,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo sam čuo od jednog crkvenjaka dok sam bio u Lubinhajgenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:01:02.50,Dialogue,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čitav karavan je napadnut pre dve nedelje.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.50,0:01:05.87,Dialogue,Man D,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, strašno... Nije li strašno?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.32,0:01:09.10,Dialogue,Man D,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toliko se plašim da ću još da pijem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:11.23,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zapamtiću tu priču.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:16.32,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moliću se, za tebe, da taj čarobnjak nije žensko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.04,0:01:18.09,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:20.68,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čini se da tebe žene mogu lako da prevare,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.68,0:01:22.52,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}da ne pominjemo kako se ponašaš posle toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:28.33,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Od kako se ono desilo počeo si da piješ više alkohola.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:32.05,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hej...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:36.03,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U skoro svakoj krčmi koju smo posetili se pričalo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:37.88,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}o Medio trgovini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.22,0:01:44.43,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Muškarci su stvarno glupa stvorenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.43,0:01:46.63,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izvini što sam glup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:51.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Vuk i prava ravnoteža
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.54,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kakav dosadan grad!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:56.52,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Krčma se zatvara prerano!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.52,0:01:59.68,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, ovim mestom upravlja administracija pobožnog grada Lubinhajgena.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:02.19,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Budi zahvalna što uopšte postoji krčma za putnike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.94,0:02:08.06,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li ovaj grad ne interesuje ništa sem vođenja pokornog života i svakodnevnih molitvi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.06,0:02:14.07,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo mesto je najbolje poznato po podužim, uspavljujućim besedama o crkvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.86,0:02:17.93,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije mi uopšte jasno šta je tu zabavno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:23.15,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Krećemo za Lubinhajgen čim prodam biber i kupim nova dobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.90,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je li to veliko mesto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:27.57,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, veće od Patsia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:29.25,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Više je grad nego mesto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.72,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Živahno je i ima mnogo radnji na otvorenom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:33.47,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hoće li biti jabuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:35.41,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nisam siguran da će imati išta kvraljivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:38.43,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo je sezona za konzervirano voće.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:40.51,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Konzervirano?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.26,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne mislim na ukiseljena dobra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.85,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Voće očuvano u medu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.63,0:02:45.77,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.77,0:02:47.09,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I to ne samo jabuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:49.34,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kruške očuvane u medu su takođe ukusne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:52.25,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A od skoro ima i breskvi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.25,0:02:53.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Breskve...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.42,0:02:58.07,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sitno seckane breskve se slažu unutar bureta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:01.82,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prvoklasni proizvodi sadrže i smokve i badem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:07.92,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pošto se med sipa na breskve, dodaje se đumbir. Onda ih tako čuvaju po dva meseca.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:15.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Njihov sladak ukus koji ti ispunjava usta kao da nije sa ovog sveta.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.64,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije začuđujuće da je čak crkva jednom razmatrala i da ih zabrani.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.54,0:03:22.00,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, balaviš.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.29,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ti me ne lažeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:31.40,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne lažem, ali obično su rezervisane za bogate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.40,0:03:33.68,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U svakom slučaju, retkost su na tržištu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.68,0:03:37.50,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Š-Šta ćeš učiniti ako se budu prodavale?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:40.06,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U-U redu, kupiću ti ih.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:41.53,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stvarno?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali samo malo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.37,0:03:45.50,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je obećanje, razumeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.83,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}H-Hej, slušaš li me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.67,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idemo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idemo odmah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.00,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gde idemo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.00,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gde drugde?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:56.93,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Idemo do gostionice po naša kola i onda idemo do te neke trgovine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.22,0:04:01.55,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Probudićemo upravitelja, prodati biber po dobroj ceni, i krenuti ka Lubinhajgenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:03.81,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čekaj malo. U ovo doba noći?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.79,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možda se prodaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:07.35,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To bi bila totalna katastrofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:11.72,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šanse da ih uopšte ne bude su veće nego da se rasprodaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:14.61,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Breskve i med, u to je teško poverovati.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:16.15,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne može biti istina.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.85,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali to je samo ako budemo imali sreće, razumeš?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:20.62,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mada,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.37,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne bi mi smetale ni kruške.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.28,0:04:31.88,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pastorova propoved je istinski dirnula naša srca.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.88,0:04:36.34,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je stvarno bio blagoslov od Boga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:43.05,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Njegove reči su nas podstakle da stremimo većim visinama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.07,0:04:48.32,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, malo sam odlutao. Hajde da se vratimo poslu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.80,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hajde.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.19,0:04:53.14,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta imate da nam ponudite danas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.81,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:57.16,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Biber, je li?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:04:59.46,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kako ste znali?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.54,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zbog mirisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:07.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Impresivno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:08.77,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije, nije.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:11.80,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dođe vam prirodno kada se bavite ovim poslom dugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.80,0:05:16.52,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da nemate kojim slučajem vagu pri sebi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:24.72,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemam, ali imam vere u Boga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.95,0:05:31.95,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U svakom slučaju, baš nemam sreće.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.95,0:05:35.23,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tražnja za biberom se značajno povećala u zadnje vreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:40.74,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da ste došli samo nedelju dana ranije, mogao sam da ga kupim jeftinije.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.61,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mora da sam došao u pravo vreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:48.55,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Svakako. Hajde onda da krenemo sa merenjem bibera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.21,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, izvolite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:54.89,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Trebaće nam papir i mastilo. Izvinite me na trenutak.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:01.50,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.38,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Žedna sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.53,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Budi strpljiva.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:15.68,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hoćete malo vode?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.19,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Imam i vina.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:20.66,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, mogu li da dobijem vode?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:22.57,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nema problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.58,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To mu dođe srazmerno sa četrdeset i pet mera.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.89,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koje je poreklo ovog bibera?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.34,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Biber je iz Ramapate iz Kraljevstva Lidon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:39.88,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Milone trgovina je obavila uvoz.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:46.50,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ramapata je poznata po svojim začinima,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:49.50,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}i ova potvrda izgleda ispravno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:56.46,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta kažete na jedan Lumione zlatnik po meri?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.46,0:06:59.91,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Koliki je kurs za Lumione zlatnike?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.91,0:07:03.41,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li želite da budete isplaćeni u Torenijevim srebrnjacima?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.41,0:07:04.07,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.07,0:07:09.76,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kurs je trideset sedam i pet šestina Toreni srebrnjaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.64,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Toliko ćemo da vam platimo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.43,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prihvatam ponudu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.43,0:07:23.24,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, onda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.34,0:07:27.92,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta nije u redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.64,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vrti mi se u glavi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:33.10,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}D-Da li ste dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.74,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}D-Da...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.39,0:07:38.18,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li se osećate bolje?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.10,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, hvala.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:43.70,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Verovatno ste se umorili od dugog putovanja.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.70,0:07:46.40,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Doneću vam malo mleka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:47.99,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gospodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:54.25,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da je prizor pred mojim očima nakrivljen iz nekog razloga.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.72,0:07:57.84,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kako izgleda vašim očima?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:01.90,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne, svakako nije nakrivljen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:04.92,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne bi trebalo da je moguće, ali...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:08.84,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, jesi li dobro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.71,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Vidim nešto što ne bi trebalo da je moguće.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:24.34,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da mi je dato vino umesto vode.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.57,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nije li tako, gospodine?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:35.11,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kao što kaže izreka, "Što je krčma pijanija, to je krčmar trezniji."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:36.26,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sada razumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:41.46,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Očigledno je da čovek mora ostati trezan da bi uspešno poslovao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.68,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da sam i ja bio malo opijen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:48.27,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Verovatno ću zaboraviti neke od stvari koje sam video i čuo ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:52.26,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali, poznato je da pijanice znaju da nepromišljeno izlaju stvari.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.30,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Š-Šta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:09:00.00,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Platićete mi ugovorenu cenu, zatim ono što ste nameravali da zaradite na meni, i...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:03.58,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}dozvolićete mi da kupim na kredit dva puta više dobara nego što smo se dogovorili.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:06.76,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Duplo? To je previše!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:09.09,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, šteta.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:11.19,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da počinjem da se treznim.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.73,0:09:14.81,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hajde da razgovaramo o robi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:18.79,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pošto je suma poveća, recimo da mi platite visoko kvalitetnim oklopima?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:21.10,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oklopi, kažete?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:26.77,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je pouzdana roba koja će zagarantovano obezbediti profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.77,0:09:29.64,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moći ću da otplatim svoje dugove sa tom robom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:33.05,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Siguran sam da skladištite dosta robe za prodaju u Lubinhajgenu, zar ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.64,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oklopi, kažete?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:39.62,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sigurno ste u dobrim odnosima sa drugim trgovcima iz Lubinhajgenu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:42.56,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Spreman sam da poremetim balans tako što ću prodati dobra njima.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.69,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta kažete na to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:49.64,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Puno vam hvala.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:52.89,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Molim vas da što pre obezbedite robu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.72,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Želeo bih da krenem za Lubinhajgen što je pre moguće.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.72,0:09:57.41,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}D-Dobro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.61,Dialogue,Appraiser,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A procena robe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:03.33,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prepustiću to vama. Ja imam vere u Boga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.06,0:10:16.53,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Siroti čovek.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.53,0:10:19.37,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Iznenađen sam da si primetila.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:23.30,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moj izgled, moja pamet i krzno na mom repu ne gube od nikoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.07,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isto važi i za moj sluh i vid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.07,0:10:28.32,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Primetila sam čim smo kročili ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.32,0:10:29.07,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.42,0:10:31.45,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta to treba da znači?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:33.41,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta ti je, odjednom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:38.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Iskustvo vodi samouverenosti, a to ponekad može da bude smrtonosno.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:40.24,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar nisi ništa naučio iz incidenta sa Kloe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.32,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U potpunosti si u pravu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.32,0:10:44.30,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Budalo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:47.24,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Samo činiš stvari gorim kada si tako mrzovoljan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:49.65,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uči iz iskustva i nastavi dalje.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:01.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ulje?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.93,0:11:05.51,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, čujem da je dobro za timarenje mog repa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.12,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Možeš li mi kupiti malo kada stignemo do sledećeg grada?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:15.59,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jesi li ikada razmišljala o ceni odeće koju nosiš, rezervne odeće, češlja,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.59,0:11:20.49,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}o putnim troškovima, hrani i računima za sve piće koje popiješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.18,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tu su i lični porezi koje plaćamo pri ulasku u grad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:27.70,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li je prosta matematika previše za tebe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.19,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umem da sabiram.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.19,0:11:32.99,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dobra sam i u oduzimanju.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:36.30,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako je tako, saberi koliko mi duguješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:39.30,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ako si mudra koliko tvrdiš da jesi, trebalo bi da znaš na šta ciljam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.14,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Znam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.75,0:11:47.02,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Znam da ćeš mi kupiti još.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:50.94,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čak i mudri vuk kao što si ti postane jadan kada je pijan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:54.15,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nisam pijana, znaš.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Budalo! Šta to radiš...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:57.99,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šalim se.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:00.32,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hej, ti...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.85,0:12:04.61,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemoj da me potcenjuješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:09.09,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Misliš li da nisam primetila kada si dobio više nego što si očekivao,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:12.09,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}iskoristivši slabost onog trgovca?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:15.08,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hoćeš li mi kupiti ulje?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:19.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li znaš koliko mi još novca duguješ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.28,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sto četrdeset srebrnjaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.91,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Siguran sam da znaš da je to pravo malo bogatstvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.91,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kako očekuješ da ti povrh toga još kupujem neke tričarije?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:32.11,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta je? Da li toliko želiš da ti isplatim svoj dug?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na -  ra -  vno!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:39.75,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Znači stvarno si tako mislio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:41.41,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na šta misliš?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:47.38,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, kada otplatim dugove, slobodna sam da činim kako želim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:52.27,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, dobro. Trebalo bi što pre da ti platim i da se zaputim ka severu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:55.09,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ionako sam se navikla da budem sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.78,0:13:03.54,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nisam još odredio rok za otplatu duga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:06.82,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Biće u redu ako mi platiš u celosti pre nego što stignemo do šuma na severu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:09.28,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da li se slažeš sa time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:15.11,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, sigurno ću moći da ti vratitm dug dok stignemo do šuma na severu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.07,0:13:23.78,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Osim toga, razmišljam da ti dodam i kamatu na ono što ti dugujem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:29.50,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Drugim rečima, što ti više dugujem, više ćeš profitirati. U redu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.52,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ulje, je li?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:38.07,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da. Možeš ga uračunati u moj dug, pa mi kupi malo, hoćeš li?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.20,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dogovoreno.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:46.37,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hvala ti.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.86,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kakav divan dan za doterivanje.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:16.63,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nego, zar nisi dobio priličan popust na ova dobra?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:18.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto pitaš?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:24.29,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pomislih da možda nije najbolja ideja da živim na grbači siromašnog putujućeg trgovca.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:27.24,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oklopi su roba koja se najbrže prodaje u Lubinhajgenu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:29.31,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ali ima i dosta trgovaca koji ih prodaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:32.29,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tu nema mnogo prilika za zaradu,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.64,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}tako da nije ni bitno da li sam dobio popust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:37.96,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali zar nećeš zaraditi pošto si kupio veliku količinu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:43.22,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, pokriću bar troškove za ulje.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:45.45,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je dobro čuti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:51.18,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali kad pogledaš, začini su jako dobri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.18,0:14:52.42,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Probao si ih?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:54.63,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nemoj da me spuštaš na tvoj nivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.63,0:14:55.90,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Govorim o njihovoj profitabilnosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:59.64,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto ne trguješ začinima opet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:02.90,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prodajna cena oklopa je ista bilo u Lubinhajgenu ili u Porosonu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.90,0:15:04.99,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na začinima bih izgubio zbog poreza.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.99,0:15:07.22,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Onda ništa od toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.22,0:15:13.23,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kada bih na drugoj robi zarađivao kao na začinima, brzo bih skupio pare da otvorim radnju.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.92,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar nema nečega na čemu bi mogao tako zaraditi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.92,0:15:20.10,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Na primer, dijamanti i zlato bi se verovatno dobro prodavali.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:23.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takve stvari nisu previše profitabilne u Lubinhajgenu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.53,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.25,0:15:31.18,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Porezi su isuviše veliki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:36.42,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uvezeno zlato koje ne pripada odabranoj grupi trgovaca je podložno visokim porezima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:38.85,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Iz tog razloga ne vredi trgovati njime.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:42.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zašto su neki trgovci izuzeti od poreza?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.49,0:15:45.26,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Imaju veze sa crkvom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:50.18,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kada tamo uvezu zlatne poluge, na njih se utiska Sveti žig.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.18,0:15:53.78,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takvo zlato biva blagosloveno prvoklasnom cenom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:57.85,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U zamenu za to, crkva dobija izdašne priloge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.23,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kvarno.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:04.67,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zato su izuzetno strogi po pitanju krijumčarenja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:09.83,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Prokrijumčarena dobra se prodaju po duplo većim cenama,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:11.77,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ali uz njih ide veliki rizik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:15.05,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zato uglavnom nema budala koje bi se okušale u tome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.40,0:16:18.17,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Zar je tako teško sakriti nešto kao što je zlato?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.92,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tamošnje kontrole tovara su prilično temeljne.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:24.25,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta bude kada te uhvate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.25,0:16:27.39,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U najgorem slučaju, odseku ti ruku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.78,0:16:30.59,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jednostavno nije vredno toga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:37.72,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, tvoj posao ide solidno. Nema ništa loše u tome da postepeno napreduješ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:43.43,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Upravo. A ko je taj što troši moj, s mukom zarađen, novac?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:16:59.25,Dialogue,Merchant,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bolje da budete pažljivi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.30,0:17:04.94,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Izgleda da su došli plaćenici sa severa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Plaćenici?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:07.01,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:11.57,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kretanje dalje ovim putem bi onda bilo samoubistvo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.57,0:17:15.60,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Da, oni spaze svoj plen brže od orla
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.60,0:17:19.22,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}i otimaju sve od vrednosti, ne ostavljajući ništa za sobom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:22.56,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A i naoružani su dugim kopljima.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:25.93,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čak i za mene je to više muke nego koristi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:29.97,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Iznenađen sam što su sišli ovako daleko na jug.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:32.96,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kao i trgovci, oni uvek delaju u svom najboljem interesu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.14,0:17:37.92,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, nema svrhe o tome pričati ovde.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:42.23,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U svakom slučaju, idemo za Lubinhajgen novim putem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.39,0:17:46.51,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne plašiš se valjda neznabožačkih čarobnjaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.51,0:17:47.36,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.84,0:17:50.75,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažu da na ovom putu ima čopora vukova.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:52.49,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oni su manji problem od ljudi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.10,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sa njima bar mogu da se sporazumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.84,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Onda ću tebi prepustiti pregovore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:11.43,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ali baš nema nikoga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.43,0:18:14.17,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažu da glasine brzo putuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:20.12,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Dosadno. Ja ću da dremnem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.59,0:18:23.77,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hoćeš li moći da osetiš vukove i ako zaspiš?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.77,0:18:25.84,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Naravno da hoću!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.84,0:18:28.20,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bilo bi gadno da nas okruže.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.20,0:18:30.09,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Previše se brineš.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.09,0:18:33.99,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Što se tiče nas životinja, nema neke razlike da li spavamo ili ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:37.28,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ljudi su previše ranjivi kada spavaju.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:40.15,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To nije baš ubedljivo kada kaže neko ko hrče u snu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.52,0:18:42.62,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja ne hrčem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.12,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pa, nisi baš toliko glasna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.12,0:18:46.82,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažem ti da ne hrčem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.82,0:18:48.49,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Razumem, razumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:50.30,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uopšte ne hrčem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:53.36,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kažem ti da razumem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:56.87,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta je bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:19:01.02,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Odavde ću prepustiti priču tebi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:05.84,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ko je ispred nas?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.57,0:19:08.89,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ljudi koje mrzim.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:11.30,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Čarobnjak o kom smo pričali?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.57,0:19:33.03,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovce?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.11,0:19:39.38,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Je li to taj čarobnjak?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.68,Dialogue,Horo,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Šta je to bilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.68,0:19:57.34,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To je ritual kada sretneš pastira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.34,0:20:00.47,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bar znamo da nije čarobnjak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.60,0:20:03.92,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ja sam putujući trgovac, Lorens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.92,0:20:05.68,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ovo je moja saputnica, Horo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:10.41,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Želim da zamolim pastira kog sam sreo vođen božjom rukom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.41,0:20:13.16,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}da se pomoli za našu bezbednost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.43,0:20:18.45,Dialogue,Norah,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Biće mi drago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.81,0:20:44.15,Dialogue,Lawrence,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sledeća epizoda, "Vuk i pastirovo stado".
